### 8. Trade-offs

| Aspect | Trade-off |
|--------|-----------|
| ClassLoader Isolation | Extra memory overhead per module, more complex debugging |
| Offline-First | Stale manifest risk, more local storage used |
| Battery-Conscious | Slower feature availability (waits for WiFi/charging) |
| Rollback | User may experience brief unavailability during rollback |
| Version Compatibility | Maintaining backward compatibility limits refactoring |

The base module should always contain minimal fallback UI/logic for critical features to ensure the app remains functional during module issues.

